					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">My solution would be probably randomizing position again until it isn't near the player or in a wall.<br /><br />So the algorithm would be (in pseudo code)<br /><br />1. Randomize enemy's position<br />2. If the enemy is in the wall or too close to player, go to 1, else carry on.</div>

